label: AT2G22430
pvalue: Encodes a homeodomain leucine zipper class I (HD-Zip I) protein that is a target of the protein phosphatase ABI1 and regulates hormone responses in Arabidopsis.

label: AT3G01220
pvalue: Encodes a homeodomain leucine zipper class I (HD-Zip I) protein.  Expressed during seed germination in the micropylar endosperm and in the root cap, and increases ABA sensitivity and seed dormancy when mutated. The mRNA is cell-to-cell mobile.
